'''飛馬座EQ'''（EQ Peg / GJ 896 / HIP 116132）<ref name=SIMBAD1>[http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=CCDM%20J23319%2B1956%20A EQ Pegasi - Flare star] ([[SIMBAD|SIMBAD]])</ref>是在[[飛馬座|飛馬座]]的一個恆星系統，距離[[太陽系|太陽系]]只有20.7[[光年|光年]]，屬於接近太陽系前100名之內的恆星系<ref name=RECONS>[http://www.chara.gsu.edu/RECONS/TOP100.posted.htm The One Hundred Nearest Star Systems]  {{webarchive|url=https://www.webcitation.org/67eTwFUKg?url=http://www.chara.gsu.edu/RECONS/TOP100.posted.htm |date=2012-05-14 }} ([[RECONS|RECONS]])</ref>。距離這個系統最近的恆星系統是[[葛利澤880|葛利澤880]]，相距僅有3.96年<ref>[http://www.stellar-database.com/Scripts/find_neighbors.exe?ID=219100&ly=15 Stars within 15 light-years of EQ Pegasi (The Internet Stellar Database)]</ref>。

飛馬座EQ是由兩顆[[紅矮星|紅矮星]]組成的[[聯星|聯星]]，'''飛馬座EQ A'''（EQ Peg A / GJ 896 A / LHS 3965）<ref name=SIMBAD1 />的光譜類型為M3.5V，[[視星等|視星等]]+10.38，有效溫度3,280[[熱力學溫標|K]]<ref name=Morales>{{cita publicación
| autor = Morales, J. C.; Ribas, I.; Jordi, C.
| título = The effect of activity on stellar temperatures and radii
| año = 2008
| publicación = [[Astronomy_and_Astrophysics|Astronomy and Astrophysics]]
| volumen = 478
| número = 2
| id = pp. 507-512 (Tabla consultada en CDS)
| url = http://cdsads.u-strasbg.fr/cgi-bin/nph-bib_query?2008A%26A...478..507M&db_key=AST&nosetcookie=1
}}</ref>。它的質量相當於1/3[[太陽質量|太陽質量]]<ref name=RECONS />，半徑約為38%的[[太陽半徑|太陽半徑]]<ref name="RECONS"></ref><ref>[http://cdsarc.u-strasbg.fr/cgi-bin/VizieR-5?-out.add=.&-source=II/224/cadars&recno=11689 Catalogue of Stellar Diameters (CADARS) (Pasinetti-Fracassini+ 2001)]</ref>。它的[[恆星自轉|自轉速度]]很高，為每秒14公里，互繞公轉週期為1,066天<ref name=Liefke />。

它的伴星，'''飛馬座EQ B'''（EQ Peg B / GJ 896 B / LHS 3966）<ref>[http://simbad.u-strasbg.fr/simbad/sim-id?Ident=CCDM%20J23319%2B1956%20B LHS 3966 - High proper-motion Star] ([[SIMBAD|SIMBAD]])</ref>，光譜類型為M4.5V，質量大約是0.16-0.19太陽質量，視星等+12.40，飛馬座EQ A比它亮8-10倍<ref name=RECONS /><ref name=Bonfils />。它的溫度為3,080K<ref name=Morales />，半徑是太陽的23% <ref>[http://cdsarc.u-strasbg.fr/cgi-bin/VizieR-5?-out.add=.&-source=II/224/cadars&recno=11690 Catalogue of Stellar Diameters (CADARS) (Pasinetti-Fracassini+ 2001)]</ref>。自轉速度高達每秒24.2公里，與飛馬座EQ A互繞著公轉<ref name=Liefke />。

這兩顆恆星相距6[[弧分|角秒]]<ref name=Bonfils>{{cita publicación
| autor = Bonfils, X.; Delfosse, X.; Udry, S.; Santos, N. C.; Forveille, T.; Ségransan, D.
| título = Metallicity of M dwarfs. I. A photometric calibration and the impact on the mass-luminosity relation at the bottom of the main sequence
| año = 2005
| publicación = [[Astronomy_and_Astrophysics|Astronomy and Astrophysics]]
| volumen = 442
| número = 2
| id = pp. 635-642
| url = http://cdsads.u-strasbg.fr/cgi-bin/nph-bib_query?2005A%26A...442..635B&db_key=AST&nosetcookie=1
}}</ref>，系統的軌道週期可能是359天<ref name=Heintz>{{cita publicación
| autor = Heintz, W. D.
| título = Orbits of 16 visual binaries
| año = 1984
| publicación = [[The_Astronomical_Journal|The Astronomical Journal]]
| volumen = 89
| número = 
| id = (ISSN 0004-6256) pp. 1063-1067
| url = http://cdsads.u-strasbg.fr/cgi-bin/nph-bib_query?1984AJ.....89.1063H&db_key=AST&nosetcookie=1
}}</ref>。
飛馬座EQ A的[[金屬量|金屬量]]豐度似乎高過太陽20%<ref name=Bonfils />，估計年齡在9億5,000萬年<ref name=Liefke>{{cita publicación
| autor = Liefke, C.; Ness, J.-U.; Schmitt, J. H. M. M.; Maggio, A.
| título = Coronal properties of the EQ Pegasi binary system
| año = 2008
| publicación = [[Astronomy_and_Astrophysics|Astronomy and Astrophysics]]
| volumen = 491
| número = 3
| id = pp. 859-872
| url = http://cdsads.u-strasbg.fr/cgi-bin/nph-bib_query?2008A%26A...491..859L&db_key=AST&nosetcookie=1
}}</ref>。
以[[X射線|X射線]]和[[紫外線|超紫外線]]觀測，這兩顆恆星可能是[[耀星|閃光星]]<ref name=Liefke />。

